  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK695">
<l>epporuḷu mōrār toṭarārmaṟ ṟapporuḷai</l>
<l>viṭṭakkāṟ kēṭka maṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(When the king is engaged) in secret counsel (with others), ministers should neither over-hear anything whatever nor pry into it with inquisitive questions, but (wait to) listen when it is divulged (by the king himself).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
